{"id":"as-tz8wsgfnq9","object":"chat.completion","created":1693142065,"result":"In today's rapidly changing world, it is important to be aware of the potential risks and consequences of certain actions. When it comes to signing legal documents, it is crucial to carefully read and understand the terms and conditions involved.

